{"tid":1896455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB客仔 Expedia將裁員約3,000人","createTime":"2020-02-25T06:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T06:51:41.000Z","uid":10757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f97da6ebecd1d3818bb7c86489a2cba9a3f992a","tid":1896455,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"全球最大網上旅行社Expedia宣布將會裁員3000人，佔總員工數目12%，同時還將終止部分項目並減少承包商及供應商來削減成本。<br />\n<br />\n被裁減的3000人，包括西雅圖總部的500名員工，預計可以節省3億至5億美元的成本，被解僱的職員本周會陸續收到通知。<br />\n<br />\nExpedia主席Barry Diller在2月初的第四季業績電話會議上批評公司架構及工作文化僵硬兼臃腫，認為員工只懂享樂不會工作，公司目標是要節省3至5億美元的營運成本。<br />\n<br />\nExpedia目前在全球有大約25400名員工，集團並無提到今次裁員與疫情有關，只是說集團需要精簡臃腫的架構，回復更健康及有紀律的增長。<br />\n<br />\n搵你老母用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cac14c724965fa75003f244679417eabce38388","tid":1896455,"uid":53481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<br />\n汰弱留強"},{"pid":"c0f8e93a5cde2a30b1f0e4d3bfc0f0c604978757","tid":1896455,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"藍底"},{"pid":"1732bf7c8f942ecb95b7caae40bb0ec655935e34","tid":1896455,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"炒晒支那人未"},{"pid":"70765fc0bf0b5f671a86559dbf3160015f249783","tid":1896455,"uid":52288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"抵死 係tvb 賣廣告<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個friend入埋做好似成日都剩係玩"},{"pid":"7bbc457e94c341b2b8852f0079b18f6a8af4133a","tid":1896455,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"係唔係搵錯代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}